           \u003Cdimensions>\n                                        \u003Cheight unit=\"cm\">15.7\u003C/height>\n                                        \u003Cwidth unit=\"cm\">24.8\u003C/width>\n                                        \u003Cdepth unit=\"cm\">2.4\u003C/depth>\n                                    \u003C/dimensions>\n                                \u003C/support>\n                                \u003Ccondition/>\n\t\t    \u003C/supportDesc>\n                            \u003ClayoutDesc>\n                                \u003Clayout>\u003Cp>Five lines of latin letters with guidelines marked out for a sixth also. The text is centred, but slightly off the horizontal; hedera/interpuncts mark the line ends.\u003C/p>\n                                    \u003Crs ana=\"#execution.chiselled\" ref=\"http://www.eagle-network.eu/voc/writing/lod/1\">chiselled\u003C/rs>\n                                \t\u003Cdamage/>\n\t\t\t\u003C/layout>\n                            \u003C/layoutDesc>\n                        \u003C/objectDesc>\n                        \u003ChandDesc>\n                            \u003ChandNote>\u003Cp>The letters show the beginnings of a shift towards the later cursive style, with extended serifs on the A and M, T tending to be narrow with upward sloping head, E likewise tall, narrow, with top stroke sloping upwards. Interpuncts, sometimes in the form of hedera, used between all words except after Calbentius\u003C/p>\n                                \u003Clocus from=\"line1\" to=\"line1\">Line 1\u003C/locus>\n                                \u003Cdimensions type=\"letterHeight\">\n                                    \u003Cheight unit=\"mm\" atLeast=\"10\" atMost=\"11\">10-11\u003C/height>\n                                \u003C/dimensions>\n                                \u003Clocus from=\"line2\" to=\"line2\">Line 2\u003C/locus>\n                                \u003Cdimensions type=\"letterHeight\">\n                                    \u003Cheight unit=\"mm\" atLeast=\"11\" atMost=\"13\">11-13\u003C/height>\n                                \u003C/dimensions>\n                                \u003Clocus from=\"line3\" to=\"line3\">Line 3\u003C/locus>\n                                \u003Cdimensions type=\"letterHeight\">\n                                    \u003Cheight unit=\"mm\" atLeast=\"10\" atMost=\"13\">10-13\u003C/height>\n                                \u003C/dimensions>\n                                \u003Clocus from=\"line4\" to=\"line4\">Line 4\u003C/locus>\n                                \u003Cdimensions type=\"letterHeight\">\n                                    \u003Cheight unit=\"mm\" atLeast=\"11\" atMost=\"13\">11-13\u003C/height>\n                                \u003C/dimensions>\n                                \u003Clocus from=\"line5\" to=\"line5\">Line 5\u003C/locus>\n                                \u003Cdimensions type=\"letterHeight\">\n                                    \u003Cheight unit=\"mm\" atLeast=\"11\" atMost=\"14\">11-14\u003C/height>\n                                \u003C/dimensions>\n                                \u003Clocus from=\"line1\" to=\"line2\">Interlineation line 1 to 2\u003C/locus>\n                                \u003Cdimensions type=\"interlinear\">\n                                    \u003Cheight unit=\"mm\" atLeast=\"11\" atMost=\"11\">11\u003C/height>\n                                \u003C/dimensions>\n                                \u003Clocus from=\"line2\" to=\"line3\">Interlineation line 2 to 3\u003C/locus>\n                                \u003Cdimensions type=\"interlinear\">\n                                    \u003Cheight unit=\"mm\" atLeast=\"5\" atMost=\"8\">5-8\u003C/height>\n                                \u003C/dimensions>\n                                \u003Clocus from=\"line3\" to=\"line4\">Interlineation line 3 to 4\u003C/locus>\n                                \u003Cdimensions type=\"interlinear\">\n            